Model

Class InhousePart

  • java.lang.Object
    • Model.Part
      • Model.InhousePart

  • public class InhousePart
extends Part
    InhousePart inherits from the Part base class. InhouseParts contain all of the Part data members plus a machineID, representing the ID of the machine used to make the part.
    See Also:
